2002-05-20  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	Fixes #82140.

	* libgnome/gnome-help.c (gnome_help_display_with_doc_id): Clarified
	error messages.  De-convoluted function a bit.  Made it check for
	the stat() return value.  Made it check for device and inode
	numbers instead of just inode number in the fallback code.
	(locate_help_file): Use g_build_filename() so that we don't get
	duplicated slashes, which yelp warns about.

	* doc/reference/libgnome-sections.txt: Added
	gnome_help_display_with_doc_id.

