	* libgnome/gnome-desktop.xmldb: New file.

	* libgnome/gnome-url.c: Use bonobo-config instead of gnome-config.

	* libgnome/libgnome-init.h (gnome_get_config_database): New function.

	* libgnome/Makefile.am (libgnome_headers): Don't install gnome-config.h.
	(libgnome_src): Removed gnome-triggers.c.

	* libgnome/libgnome.h: Don't #include <libgnome/gnome-config.h>.

